  m_text: "Runtime-animated SDF effects on a batched UGUI canvas. The Gallery shows
    the library; the Playground lets you DRIVE an effect live with sliders (signal-bound,
    zero UnityEvents); Combos puts them on real UI. Tier-1 effects (glow, sheen,
    gradient, spinner, morph, ring, rainbow, juice) stay on the ONE shared NeoShape
    material \u2014 zero extra draw calls. Tier-2 (dissolve, holo-foil, glitch) opt
    into their own shader."
